## 3. Repository Structure

configs/
Input configuration files for all test cases

data/
Generated outputs (CSV files, plots, error tables). This directory is not tracked by git

src/
Core implementation

- app/
  Entry point for the solver

- euler/
  Numerical methods, fluxes, reconstruction, and solvers

- graphing/
  Plotting utilities and L1 error computation

- io/
  Configuration handling and CSV output

- math/
  Supporting numerical utilities

- setup/
